    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Rot grubs are pale, segmented creatures the size of a fist — the physical manifestation of the Rot's hunger. They dissolve stone and mortar on contact. Appearing in coordinated swarms of 8–12, they act as a single unit that must be dealt with through area attacks; targeting individuals only splits and scatters them. Each gnaw at Foundation damage can compromise walls, and enough accumulated damage will collapse fortifications entirely — exactly what the undead assault requires.</p>",
        "public": ""
